                <note rend="inline" type="source">815.00/2710: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Honduras</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morales</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-10-17T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 17, 1923—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>45. Your October 11, 8 p.m. Department is gratified to receive information
                    conveyed. Telegram referred to in your October 8, 7 p.m., has been given to the
                    press.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
